Override documentation
======================
## e.g. 
## XYZ -- This residue has a bad annotation of ....


# Note: The following haven't been edited for scientific accuracy, just merely to keep Rosetta from crashing when it uses them
7HA -- Leaving group annotations which leaves a disconnected type; fix annotations
GOM -- Leaving group annotations which leaves a disconnected type; fix annotations
NKS -- Leaving group annotations which leaves a disconnected type; fix annotations
THX -- Leaving group annotations which leaves a disconnected type; fix annotations
 
